data.description: Welcome to this stunning home in Sienna Hills! This beautiful property features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, perfect for a growing family or those who enjoy having extra space. As you step inside, you'll be immediately impressed by the upgrades and attention to detail. The kitchen is a true highlight, with its gorgeous granite countertops, recessed canned lighting, and 42'' cabinets with crown molding. The primary suite is equipped with a ceiling fan and plenty of natural light, this room is both stylish and comfortable. The ensuite bathroom features a dual sink vanity, and  huge walk-in closet. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home!
